metadata.name: "Set Me Free"
metadata.description:
The photo was a self-portrait clicked in 2012. I was trying to escape the never-ending questions in my head that I couldn't figure out the answers to. 
Two photos overlayed resulted in something that I could connect from my soul. The urge to "set me free".

After 10 years I find myself in a similar situation. 
In desperation and hope! 

Dedicated to the importance of Mental Health.
